                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-primary mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong class="text-gray-900">Fire Payı ve Montaj Zorluğu:</strong> 
